des:
B96 The Block, ¨Atl’s Hottest Station in the Streets¨ is Dedicated to playing the best in Today’s Music, Throwbacks and Classics. 

Whether you are tuning in to provide a soundtrack for your daily activities, tuning in to create lasting memories at an event or just trying to get through your work day, If you like good music “B96 The Block” is your Station!

From Exclusive, cutting edge interviews, Hot Topics, Informative News, Community Outreach and some of the Best DJ Mix Shows on the airwaves, B96 The Block is dedicated to representing the best in broadcasting and media excellence in the city.

Tune in daily to “Atl’s Hottest Station in the Street!
